UID:NGis_PjP-ufnAG2jLeNSi
SUMMARY:Break Even Bottle Program - Every Tuesday at The Cottage!
DTSTAMP:20260307T235945Z
DTSTART:20260310T230000Z
DESCRIPTION:Discover something truly exceptional every Tuesday at The Cotta
	ge with our Break Even Bottle program\, where rare and exquisite spirits a
	re yours to explore. \n\n📅 When: \n\nEvery Tuesday\n\n4:00 PM to 9:00 PM \
	\(or until the bottle is finished\\)\n\n📍 Where:\n\nThe Cottage – Bothell 
	\n\nEach week\, we open a unique and rare bottle\, offering 1oz pours at c
	ost. It’s your chance to try something extraordinary that you won’t find o
	n most menus—perfect for seasoned connoisseurs and curious tasters alike. 
	\n\nWhy Join Us?\n\n✨ Exclusive access to rare and premium spirits\n\n✨ Af
	fordable 1oz pours\n\n✨ A cozy and inviting atmosphere \n\nBring your frie
	nds and savor an evening of exceptional flavors. Don’t miss out on this un
	ique tasting experience! \n\nReservations are encouraged: https://resy.com
	/cities/bothell-wa/venues/the-cottage-bothell?date=2025-01-15&seats=2 \n\n
	Spread the word and join us for the Break Even Bottle program at The Cotta
	ge. See you Tuesday!\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/brea
	k-even-bottle-program-every-tuesday-at-the-cottage/18291557/2026-03-10T00\
	n\nFrom SEAtoday - Food & Drink
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/break-even-bottle-program
	-every-tuesday-at-the-cottage/18291557/2026-03-10T00
LOCATION:The Cottage\, 10029 NE 183rd St\, Bothell\, WA
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:seatoday-food
CATEGORIES:SEAtoday - Food & Drink
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT4H
END:VEVENT
